Simple CRM is the example application used for demonstration of 
console-based management interfaces in the blog series
"Console Based Configuration Managment with CLAP" on http://www.cajuncodemonkey.com. 
The series starts here: http://www.cajuncodemonkey.com/2012/10/console-based-configuration-management.html

Please post any questions or issues to the blog or gitbug:
https://github.com/krcourville/ConsoleBasedConfigurationManagementWithClap

Credits:
Code infrastructure is heavily used from Pluralsight's course, "Building ASP.NET MVC Apps with EF Code First, HTML5, and jQuery".